1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,880
¿Cuántas veces

2
00:00:00,880 --> 00:00:01,200
habéis pasado

3
00:00:01,200 --> 00:00:01,640
por delante

4
00:00:01,640 --> 00:00:02,040
de algo

5
00:00:02,040 --> 00:00:03,000
perfectamente bueno...

6
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:03,440
tirado en

7
00:00:03,440 --> 00:00:04,240
la acera...

8
00:00:04,240 --> 00:00:05,160
y habéis pensado

9
00:00:05,160 --> 00:00:05,880
"qué pena"?

10
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:06,600
Pues pasa

11
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:07,440
todos los días.

12
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:07,600
En todas

13
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:08,400
las ciudades.

14
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:09,040
Muebles,

15
00:00:09,040 --> 00:00:09,560
aparatos,

16
00:00:09,560 --> 00:00:10,960
cosas útiles...

17
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:12,040
ahí tiradas,

18
00:00:12,040 --> 00:00:13,120
a plena vista.

19
00:00:13,120 --> 00:00:13,600
Esperando

20
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:13,960
a que alguien

21
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:14,800
las vea.

22
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:15,480
Y lo curioso

23
00:00:15,480 --> 00:00:15,760
es que

24
00:00:15,760 --> 00:00:16,400
a unas calles

25
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:17,040
de distancia,

26
00:00:17,040 --> 00:00:17,600
hay alguien

27
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:18,680
que las necesita.

28
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:18,880
Pero no

29
00:00:18,880 --> 00:00:19,560
se enteran.

30
00:00:19,560 --> 00:00:20,200
Una cosa menos

31
00:00:20,200 --> 00:00:21,160
en la basura...

32
00:00:21,160 --> 00:00:21,960
es una cosa más

33
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:22,720
aprovechada.

34
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:23,520
Así de simple.

35
00:00:23,520 --> 00:00:24,160
Por eso

36
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:24,840
siempre llevo

37
00:00:24,840 --> 00:00:25,840
el móvil preparado.

38
00:00:25,840 --> 00:00:26,240
Givore.

39
00:00:26,240 --> 00:00:26,840
Compartes

40
00:00:26,840 --> 00:00:27,720
lo que te sobra.

41
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:28,000
Descubres

42
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:28,640
lo que otros

43
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,480
ofrecen.

44
00:00:29,480 --> 00:00:29,800
Foto,

45
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:30,440
título,

46
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:31,080
y en segundos

47
00:00:31,080 --> 00:00:31,640
ya lo ve

48
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:32,600
gente de tu zona.

49
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:33,080
Pero os soy

50
00:00:33,080 --> 00:00:33,880
sincero.

51
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:34,440
Givore acaba

52
00:00:34,440 --> 00:00:35,280
de arrancar.

53
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:36,480
La comunidad

54
00:00:36,480 --> 00:00:37,280
se está formando.

55
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:37,880
Poco a poco.

56
00:00:37,880 --> 00:00:38,960
Ciudad a ciudad.

57
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:39,640
Y cada persona

58
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:40,040
que se une

59
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:40,960
marca la diferencia.

60
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:42,280
Porque lo ideal

61
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:42,920
no es encontrar

62
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:44,040
cosas en la calle.

63
00:00:44,040 --> 00:00:44,840
Lo ideal

64
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:45,680
es que se compartan

65
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:46,720
antes de acabar ahí.

66
00:00:46,720 --> 00:00:48,000
¿Creéis en eso?

67
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:48,640
Contádmelo

68
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:49,280
en comentarios.

69
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:49,680
Quiero saber

70
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:50,560
qué pensáis.

